reviews.review_text: Patina-enriched recording A lot shakier than the previous few nights, but still amazing. Garcia seems to need a little while to get going in some cases, but given time to stretch out, he blasts off like a supernova.
Thank you Much appreciation to those involved with capturing and getting this uploaded, the only complete version of this legendary show. It sounds great too.
